headline: Fair Isaac (FICO) Is Up 11.9% After Strong 2025 Results and FICO 10T Industry Partnerships
summary: Fair Isaac Corporation recently reported strong financial results for fiscal 2025, with annual revenue rising to US$1.99 billion and net income reaching US$651.95 million, alongside new multi-year partnerships expanding the reach of FICO's credit scoring and fraud management tools across the U.S. mortgage and Swiss banking industries. These developments highlight Fair Isaac's increasing influence as regulatory bodies consider adopting its advanced FICO 10T model, and as key industry players...
